<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>웹 테스트 리포트 - {{testResult.name}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .info-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .info-card h3 {
            color: #6366f1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        }
        
        .info-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .status-success { background-color: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
        .status-danger { background-color: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626; }
        .status-warning { background-color: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; }
        .status-secondary { background-color: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; }
        
        .metrics-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .metrics-section h2 {
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .metrics-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .metric-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
        }
        
        .metric-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .metric-value {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .metric-description {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .metrics-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>웹 테스트 리포트</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">{{testResult.name}}</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>테스트 정보</h3>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">테스트 이름:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{testResult.name}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">테스트 유형:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{testType.name}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">대상 URL:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{testResult.url}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">상태:</span>
                    <span class="status-badge status-{{getStatusColor testResult.status}}">
                        {{getStatusText testResult.status}}
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>실행 정보</h3>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">시작 시간:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{formatDate testResult.summary.startTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">종료 시간:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{formatDate testResult.summary.endTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">소요 시간:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{formatDuration testResult.summary.duration}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">생성 시간:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{formatDate generatedAt}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        {{#if metrics.length}}
        <div class="metrics-section">
            <h2>성능 메트릭</h2>
            <div class="metrics-grid">
                {{#each metrics}}
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">{{this.metric_name}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{formatMetricValue this.value this.unit}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">{{this.description}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        {{#if testResult.metrics}}
        <div class="metrics-section">
            <h2>테스트 메트릭</h2>
            <div class="metrics-grid">
                {{#if testResult.metrics.http_req_duration}}
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">HTTP 요청 지속시간 (평균)</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{formatMetricValue testResult.metrics.http_req_duration.avg 'ms'}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">평균 HTTP 요청 지속시간</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">HTTP 요청 지속시간 (최대)</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{formatMetricValue testResult.metrics.http_req_duration.max 'ms'}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">최대 HTTP 요청 지속시간</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">HTTP 요청 지속시간 (95%ile)</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{formatMetricValue testResult.metrics.http_req_duration.p95 'ms'}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">95%ile HTTP 요청 지속시간</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if testResult.metrics.http_req_rate}}
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">HTTP 요청률</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{formatMetricValue testResult.metrics.http_req_rate 'req/s'}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">초당 HTTP 요청 수</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if testResult.metrics.http_req_failed}}
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">실패한 요청</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{testResult.metrics.http_req_failed}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">실패한 HTTP 요청 수</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if testResult.metrics.vus}}
                <div class="metric-card">
                    <div class="metric-name">가상 사용자</div>
                    <div class="metric-value">{{testResult.metrics.vus}}</div>
                    <div class="metric-description">현재 가상 사용자 수</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        
        {{#if testResult.description}}
        <div class="info-card">
            <h3>설명</h3>
            <p>{{testResult.description}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>이 리포트는 웹 테스팅 플랫폼에서 자동으로 생성되었습니다.</p>
        <p>리포트 ID: {{reportId}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 